This course is a
little different than

6
00:00:15.020 --> 00:00:16.430
every programming
course that I've

7
00:00:16.430 --> 00:00:18.110
ever taught, or I've ever taken.

8
00:00:18.110 --> 00:00:19.910
This course is dedicated to

9
00:00:19.910 --> 00:00:22.040
the notion that
every single person

10
00:00:22.040 --> 00:00:23.630
on the planet needs
to be able to write

11
00:00:23.630 --> 00:00:26.390
programs and can write programs.

12
00:00:26.390 --> 00:00:29.195
You do not have to
have a bunch of math.

13
00:00:29.195 --> 00:00:30.440
I do not expect math.

14
00:00:30.440 --> 00:00:31.520
I do not expect that you've taken

15
