49
00:01:45.710 --> 00:01:48.770
You've just got to like add
two spaces and it's fine."

50
00:01:48.770 --> 00:01:51.230
And you're like, "Oh, that
saved me a lot of time."

51
00:01:51.230 --> 00:01:55.085
So I want you to be willing
to help somebody else.

52
00:01:55.085 --> 00:01:57.170
Another thing that's
important to me is

53
00:01:57.170 --> 00:01:59.975
that I want to create
more teachers.

54
00:01:59.975 --> 00:02:03.030
