They're all licensed
under Creative Commons,

60
00:02:13.400 --> 00:02:15.635
the slides, the autograders.

61
00:02:15.635 --> 00:02:19.264
I want you to in a sense
adopt this textbook,

62
00:02:19.264 --> 00:02:21.350
and then use
my teaching kit so that

63
00:02:21.350 --> 00:02:23.735
you can become a teacher
of this material,

64
00:02:23.735 --> 00:02:25.220
because I don't think that I'm

65
00:02:25.220 --> 00:02:27.610
naturally the only
teacher of this.

66
00:02:27.610 --> 00:02:30.690
And in particular, if you don't

67
00:02:30.690 --> 00:02:33.295
