that you can take them,

73
00:02:42.910 --> 00:02:45.085
you can translate them
into your language.

74
00:02:45.085 --> 00:02:48.260
The book has been translated
into several languages.

75
00:02:48.260 --> 00:02:49.670
And that's really exciting.

76
00:02:49.670 --> 00:02:51.800
Those books that have
been translated are

77
00:02:51.800 --> 00:02:54.215
usually free and available.

78
00:02:54.215 --> 00:02:55.820
You can get print copies
that are very

79
00:02:55.820 --> 00:02:58.190
inexpensive and
all the ecopies are free.

80
00:02:58.190 --> 00:03:01.520
And so this notion that
I create this kit,

81
00:03:01.520 --> 00:03:03.665
that you can then change the kit.

82
00:03:03.665 --> 00:03:05.240
You don't have to
just take my class.

83
00:03:05.240 --> 00:03:06.680
You can change it and you can

84
00:03:06.680 --> 00:03:08.995
make it work for you locally.

85
00:03:08.995 --> 00:03:12.725
And really, the overall
goal of this is

86
00:03:12.725 --> 00:03:15.770
more than just like teaching
you one programming class.

87
