this sort of club where you

93
00:03:35.660 --> 00:03:38.105
need to know something
about technology.

94
00:03:38.105 --> 00:03:42.410
And so that's why we're
Programming for Everybody.

95
00:03:42.410 --> 00:03:47.045
Regardless of geography,
regardless of ability to pay,

96
00:03:47.045 --> 00:03:49.715
regardless of if you
have any disabilities,

97
00:03:49.715 --> 00:03:53.345
I want Programming for
Everybody to be everybody.

98
00:03:53.345 --> 00:03:55.970
I want when to just expand

99
00:03:55.970 --> 00:03:57.470
